      "message": "This name is weird to read, given that you just said we can\u0027t use max_align_t.  Is this, what alignment we get from new?  Let\u0027s call it guaranteed_alignment?\n\nAs for the value, I think it\u0027s typically 2*sizeof(void*).  I guess if you write alignof(double) instead of 8 here, it\u0027s more obvious we\u0027re being conservative?",
