      "message": "Both allocObject and allocObjectWithFooter return objStart, and fCursor padding before objStart. It may seem that allocObjectWithFooter is adjusting the fCursor with to compensate for the object, but really it is adding a skipFunction if it needs to. Really allocObjectWithFooter and allocObject have the same objStart and fCursor invariants.",
